REST API Design (Movies)

| HTTP Method | Endpoint     | Description                          |
| ----------- | -----------  | -----------------------------------  |
| GET         | /movies      | Retrieve all movie objects           |
| GET         | /movies/{id} | Retrieve a single movie object by id |
| POST        | /movies      | Create a new movie object            |
| PUT         | /movies/{id} | Update the entire movie object       |
| PATCH       | /movies/{id} | Update part of the movie object      |
| DELETE      | /movies/{id} | Delete a movie object                |